CHAT.comment: Home Visit 5 Chi sits on the floor leaning against a table
Once there was a troll he lived in a big hole next to the bridge and every day when the people came by he ate them. Chi [= full name]

Chi doesn't know who to write to so Mot suggests writing a story. Chi likes this idea and writes about a familiar story of a troll. Chi writes the story by herself with almost no help at all from Mot. Therefore , there are many long pauses with no conversation. Chi gets a little frustrated at times when she has to erase something she wrote. Chi has very nice hand+writing.
